    "body": "## Problem\r\n\r\n`vim.fn.writefile()` rejects Lua strings.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nRelated (possibly fixes): #35589.\r\n\r\nI looked over #31930 and addressed its review comments here; if this is the version to merge, #31930 should be closed.\r\n\r\nTo reiterate, this updates the Lua bridge so `vim.fn.writefile()`treats Lua strings like blob data while vimscript `:call writefile()` still rejects strings (as previosuly discussed).\r\n",
    "closed_at": null,
